# Kuat Design System - Agent Guidelines

## Project Structure
This is a monorepo containing:
- `@equal-experts/kuat-core`: Shared CSS variables and Tailwind configuration
- `@equal-experts/kuat-react`: React components using shadcn/ui
- `@equal-experts/kuat-vue`: Vue components using shadcn-vue

